Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,原料放映出品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉的奇妙七日\N{\fs30}VALERIE AND HER WEEK OF WONDERS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,字幕翻译制作：大傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:01:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那儿？\N{\fs30}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,黄鼠狼！\N{\fs30}Polecat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我吧\N{\fs30}forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她的耳环呢？\N{\fs30}Where are her earrings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-说！  -我弄丢了 治安官\N{\fs30}-Speak!  -I lost them, Constable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你撒谎 奥利库 你是逃不掉惩罚的\N{\fs30}You're lying, Eaglet. You won't escape punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用水刑拷问你！\N{\fs30}I'll put you to the water torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库！\N{\fs30}Eaglet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,弯腰 我要跳到你的背上\N{\fs30}Bend over so I can jump on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs30}Hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,捣蛋鬼\N{\fs30}you brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 剧团来了\N{\fs30}Grandma, the actors have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你更应该关心 传教士们要来了\N{\fs30}You should be more interested in the missionaries arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候？\N{\fs30}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天或明天\N{\fs30}Today or tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们其中一个 会住在我们家\N{\fs30}One of them will stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,用餐不要玩儿耳环 孩子\N{\fs30}Are you playing with your earring, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再是孩子了\N{\fs30}I'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 昨晚...\N{\fs30}In fact, just last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,都是在13岁...\N{\fs30}At the age of 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,和你妈妈一样\N{\fs30}just like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告你\N{\fs30}I'm warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰那耳环\N{\fs30}Get rid of those earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲 在进修道院那天 丢弃了它们\N{\fs30}Your mother put them away the day she entered the convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父亲是主教\N{\fs30}Your father was the bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 他们现在都在天堂\N{\fs30}As you know,they're both in heaven now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,耳环里藏着什么秘密吗？\N{\fs30}Is there some secret in these earrings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 没有\N{\fs30}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我从某个治安官手里买这房子的时候\N{\fs30}I got them at the auction of this house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,得到的这副耳环\N{\fs30}from a certain Constable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他吗？\N{\fs30}You knew him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 是剧团！\N{\fs30}Grandma, it's the actors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是一场婚礼\N{\fs30}No, that's a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,海德维卡结婚了\N{\fs30}Hedvika's getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,求主垂怜\N{\fs30}Kyrie ele son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊 降福于她\N{\fs30}Lord, have mercy on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,愿她出离愤怒...\N{\fs30}Deliver her from thy wrath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的海德维卡\N{\fs30}Poor Hedvika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜？\N{\fs30}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经成为地主的妻子了\N{\fs30}She'll be a rich landowner's wife now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母！\N{\fs30}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪！\N{\fs30}A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能是他\N{\fs30}It can't be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他早就死了\N{\fs30}He's dead, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说谁，祖母？\N{\fs30}Who are you talking about,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去练你的钢琴吧\N{\fs30}Go practice your scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是 祖母\N{\fs30}Yes, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,“美丽的少女...\N{\fs30}“Beautiful maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是我偷了你的耳环\N{\fs30}it was who stole your earrings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,又将它们送回你手中\N{\fs30}and then returned them into your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的叔父 治安官 一直觊觎耳环\N{\fs30}My uncle, the Constable,longs to seize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀了我的父亲和母亲\N{\fs30}He killed my father and mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 他害怕的是你\N{\fs30}and now fear for your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 在教堂\N{\fs30}In church today —
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在教堂 将举行少女训诫会\N{\fs30}In church today there will be a sermon for young maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请将你的衣裙 挂在凉亭里\N{\fs30}Please leave a dress of yours for me in the arbor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以便我伪装 去教堂找你说话\N{\fs30}that might disguise myself and speak to you in church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你可怜的奥利库”\N{\fs30}Your poor Eaglet.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉！\N{\fs30}Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪呢 孩子？\N{\fs30}Where are you, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候换衣服去教堂了\N{\fs30}It's time to dress for church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 我能带一小支迷迭香吗？\N{\fs30}Grandma, may I bring a sprig of rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我 上帝的仆人\N{\fs30}I, a servant of the Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,传教士\N{\fs30}and a missionary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 我来到你们中间 亲爱的少女们\N{\fs30}have come among you today,dear maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给你们阐释 启迪你们\N{\fs30}for your instruction and edification.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 贞洁的少女\N{\fs30}o virginal maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你们是什么吗？\N{\fs30}do you know what you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是用来敬贺的雪白的玉手\N{\fs30}You're an alabaster hand proffered in greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是未绽开的石榴\N{\fs30}You're a pomegranate yet to be split open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是微合的嫩叶\N{\fs30}You're a boat-shaped leaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是渐开的玫瑰花蕾\N{\fs30}an opening rosebud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那冰冷的手\N{\fs30}The callous hand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或将碰触你们的胸\N{\fs30}that would touch your breast
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那将留下不可磨灭的印迹\N{\fs30}would leave an indelible imprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我与你同在，我的少女们\N{\fs30}But I am here with you,my maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在守护天使之所\N{\fs30}In place of your guardian angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你们致意...\N{\fs30}I bend down to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用最精致的油膏致意\N{\fs30}and with the most exquisite ointment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福你们的唇 你们的胸...\N{\fs30}I bless your lips,your breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的腰\N{\fs30}your loins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库\N{\fs30}Eaglet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库\N{\fs30}Eaglet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是你吗？\N{\fs30}is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是那怪物把我弄成这样的\N{\fs30}That monster tortured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉 我想给你一些忠告\N{\fs30}Valerie, I want to give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们这是在广场上  -原谅我\N{\fs30}-We're in the town square.  -Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看\N{\fs30}Hide your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗？\N{\fs30}Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs30}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿\N{\fs30}Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,首先...\N{\fs30}First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,教众们的济贫院怎么走 我的好孩子？\N{\fs30}Where is the parish poorhouse,dear child?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在那边 神父\N{\fs30}Over there, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个充满仁慈的好孩子\N{\fs30}You're performing an act of mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你会介意给我指路？\N{\fs30}Or perhaps you mind taking me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意 神父\N{\fs30}Not at all, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我以主的名义 向您祈求！\N{\fs30}In God's name, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你先进去\N{\fs30}You go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走 不要怕\N{\fs30}Go on. Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临\N{\fs30}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的王国\N{\fs30}This is my kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近些\N{\fs30}come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,近些\N{\fs30}Closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 你就会看到\N{\fs30}Come and you will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs30}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不再爱我了 我的葛拉西安\N{\fs30}I know that you love me no longer, my Gracián.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一晃五年了 记得你上一次在这里...\N{\fs30}Just five years ago,when you were last here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,却如今！\N{\fs30}but now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,走开吧 你！\N{\fs30}Away with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要鞭挞己身！\N{\fs30}I'll whip myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母！\N{\fs30}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,继续看\N{\fs30}Keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一个梦\N{\fs30}This is only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡着了\N{\fs30}I'm asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切 都是梦\N{\fs30}and all this is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他伤害你了吗？\N{\fs30}Did he hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没\N{\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让你爱他\N{\fs30}He wants you to love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当我怕他的时候 如何能爱他呢？\N{\fs30}How can I love him when I'm afraid of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是关键之所在\N{\fs30}That's exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库！\N{\fs30}Eaglet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我正等着你呢 治安官\N{\fs30}I'm waiting for you,Constable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,多管闲事！\N{\fs30}Damned meddler!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手 不然我开枪了 贼人！\N{\fs30}Hands up or I'll shoot, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽莎\N{\fs30}Elsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊\N{\fs30}it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你认不出我了？\N{\fs30}Do you not recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,理查德！\N{\fs30}Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好久好久没有人这样 叫我的\N{\fs30}It's been so long since anyone called me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个名字了\N{\fs30}by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么来了 理查德？\N{\fs30}Why have you come, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你了\N{\fs30}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,自从那日 你诱奸并抛弃了我...\N{\fs30}Since the day you seduced and abandoned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我再也没有爱上别人\N{\fs30}I've never loved another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呜呼哀哉\N{\fs30}How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你已人老珠黄了 爱丽莎！\N{\fs30}How old you are now, Elsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不再是当年十七岁的妙龄\N{\fs30}You were 17 back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要我怎样 才能像你一样返老还童！\N{\fs30}What I'd give to become young again like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,理查德\N{\fs30}Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的秘密\N{\fs30}tell me your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么 我都给你！\N{\fs30}I'll give you anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要回这所房子\N{\fs30}Give me back this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这等于抢夺了瓦莱莉的房子\N{\fs30}That would be robbing Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就准备坦白你的恶行吧\N{\fs30}You're ready to commit far worse acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.22,0:24:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么我都答应\N{\fs30}I'll do anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.35,0:24:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs30}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.18,0:24:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们来签个小小的契约吧\N{\fs30}Let's draw up a little contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你将会再次拥有青春和美貌\N{\fs30}You will be young and beautiful again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就在今夜\N{\fs30}It will happen tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.90,0:24:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个吝啬地主的婚礼上\N{\fs30}at that miserly landowner's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个魔鬼！\N{\fs30}You're the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.66,0:25:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这枚珍珠会搭救你\N{\fs30}This pearl will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库 瓦莱莉在哪？\N{\fs30}Eaglet, where's Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.54,0:25:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-我把她带走了  -带哪了？\N{\fs30}-I carried her off.  -To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.75,0:25:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,教堂塔楼\N{\fs30}The church tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.80,0:25:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 你这个蠢蛋！\N{\fs30}Come here, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你也带我去塔楼！\N{\fs30}You will take me there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,祷告吧\N{\fs30}Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.80,0:26:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗？\N{\fs30}Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,钟声响三通 而后 又回归平静\N{\fs30}Three times now the bells have begun ringing and then gone silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.98,0:26:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太好吃了\N{\fs30}This is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.99,0:27:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,困苦会使人的食欲大增\N{\fs30}Hardship always leaves one with an appetite,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.28,0:27:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对此 我深有感受\N{\fs30}and I experienced a good many things
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.45,0:27:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当我去食人族中布道的时候\N{\fs30}on my mission among the cannibals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.25,0:27:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了一个黑人女孩儿\N{\fs30}We saved a young black woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.13,0:27:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她非常漂亮\N{\fs30}She was very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.21,0:27:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她后来怎么样了 神父？\N{\fs30}What became of her, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.51,0:27:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把她带回帐篷\N{\fs30}We took her to our tent
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,说服她信上帝\N{\fs30}and converted her to our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.85,0:27:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她非常有天赋\N{\fs30}She showed great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.52,0:27:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她成为修女了吗？\N{\fs30}Did she become a nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.81,0:27:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 非常可惜\N{\fs30}No, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.82,0:27:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她在法国港口走丢了\N{\fs30}We lost her in a French port.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.36,0:27:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,玛莎 酒呢？\N{\fs30}Marta, where's the wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.90,0:27:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你她后来怎么样的\N{\fs30}One day I'll tell you what became of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.57,0:27:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她堕入淫邪之路\N{\fs30}She fell into immoral ways
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.45,0:27:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,犯了第六诫 不可奸淫\N{\fs30}and sinned against the sixth commandment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在这方面 我会跟你好好说说的 亲爱的孩子\N{\fs30}I'll give you a talk on the subject, dear child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.50,0:27:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 神父\N{\fs30}Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.17,0:28:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的主教父亲 是个有修养 敏锐的人\N{\fs30}Your father,the bishop,was a refined and sensitive man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,行淫者来向他告解的时候 他会昏厥\N{\fs30}He'd faint when the prostitutes came to confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.10,0:28:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而所有美丽的女人都爱慕他\N{\fs30}and all the beautiful women adored him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.77,0:28:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找时间跟你多聊聊这些\N{\fs30}I'll tell you more some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.64,0:28:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他有几个孩子？\N{\fs30}How many children did he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.90,0:28:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有你\N{\fs30}He had you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.07,0:28:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个男孩 叫 奥利库\N{\fs30}and a boy named Eaglet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.61,0:28:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库？\N{\fs30}Eaglet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.49,0:28:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？\N{\fs30}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.12,0:28:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点头疼 我能去躺会儿吗？\N{\fs30}I have a headache. May I go lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.91,0:28:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚餐还没有结束呢  -对不起\N{\fs30}-Dinner's not over yet.  -Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.71,0:28:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你要和我们碰杯吗？\N{\fs30}Will you toast with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.42,0:28:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不喝酒\N{\fs30}I've never had wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.34,0:28:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可以例外\N{\fs30}Today will be an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.64,0:28:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,以纪念死去的主教\N{\fs30}In memory of the late bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库！\N{\fs30}Eaglet!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.57,0:29:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我来找你聊聊 亲爱的孩子\N{\fs30}I've come to speak with you,dear child.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.87,0:29:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗 神父？\N{\fs30}Now, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是最适合静思的时间啊\N{\fs30}There is no better time for contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.17,0:29:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胸真美啊！\N{\fs30}What beautiful breasts you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.42,0:30:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请您走开 神父！\N{\fs30}Please go away, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.22,0:30:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我渴求的是你的甜蜜\N{\fs30}What I desire from you is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.02,0:30:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你太可爱了\N{\fs30}You're so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.86,0:30:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-如此的高贵  -走开！\N{\fs30}-You're magnificent.  -Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.86,0:30:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让人销魂！\N{\fs30}You're ravishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.65,0:30:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我 你这个懦夫！\N{\fs30}I'll fight you off, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.74,0:30:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用死 给你良心的谴责\N{\fs30}My death will be on your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么？\N{\fs30}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.81,0:31:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是鸡瘟！\N{\fs30}The fowl plague!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.36,0:31:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡瘟降临了！\N{\fs30}The fowl plague is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.61,0:31:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,签好了\N{\fs30}It is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.62,0:31:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的房子又是你的了\N{\fs30}My house is yours again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.67,0:32:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们只等午夜...\N{\fs30}And now we will wait until midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在婚床边\N{\fs30}by the conjugal bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.01,0:32:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs30}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.34,0:32:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候了\N{\fs30}It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.18,0:33:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我所有的梦想都碎了\N{\fs30}All my dreams have come to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.53,0:33:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,来 是时候了\N{\fs30}Come. It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我老了\N{\fs30}I am old.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.05,0:33:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会老的\N{\fs30}I shall grow old too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.75,0:34:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你爱我吗？  -爱\N{\fs30}-Do you love me?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.40,0:34:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一滴血也没有\N{\fs30}Not a drop of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.07,0:34:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要哭\N{\fs30}Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.99,0:34:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当你哭时会显得苍老\N{\fs30}You look old when you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库！\N{\fs30}Eaglet!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.01,0:35:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs30}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.60,0:35:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要这样看我  -怎样？\N{\fs30}-Don't look at me like that.  -Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.19,0:35:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下\N{\fs30}Kneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.23,0:35:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下！\N{\fs30}Kneel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.37,0:36:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷吗？  -不冷\N{\fs30}-Is it too cold?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.21,0:36:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像盲人\N{\fs30}I'm like a blind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.75,0:36:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我家有一间客房空着\N{\fs30}There's an empty guest room at our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.92,0:36:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在那休息\N{\fs30}You can rest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.22,0:36:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个混蛋把我推下了塔楼\N{\fs30}That bastard threw me down from the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.26,0:36:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,敲钟绳救了我\N{\fs30}The clapper of the bell saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.35,0:36:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我听到了反常的钟响\N{\fs30}I heard it toll very oddly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.31,0:36:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为你祈祷来着\N{\fs30}I prayed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.91,0:36:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡瘟来的正是时候\N{\fs30}The plague is our best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.45,0:36:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了新鲜的血 我的治安官叔叔\N{\fs30}Without enough fresh blood,my uncle the Constable
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.96,0:36:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-会像动物一样死去  -你真冷酷！\N{\fs30}-will die like an animal.  -You're so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.67,0:36:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,几百岁的他早该死了\N{\fs30}He's been ripe for death for a hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.46,0:36:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物\N{\fs30}the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.26,0:37:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 只是一个挂在窗户上的男人\N{\fs30}It's nothing. Just a man hanging from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.40,0:37:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这是在哪啊？\N{\fs30}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.16,0:37:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就在你的房子下面\N{\fs30}Still right under your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.32,0:37:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕\N{\fs30}I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.12,0:37:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢点\N{\fs30}Be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.79,0:37:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这些棺材里都是什么人？\N{\fs30}Who's inside these coffins?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.96,0:37:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,黄鼠狼的猎物 他们的血都被吸干了 看\N{\fs30}Victims of the Polecat,their veins sucked dry. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.63,0:37:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母！\N{\fs30}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.38,0:38:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我 不得体的着装\N{\fs30}Forgive me.I wasn't suitably dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.17,0:38:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的房间\N{\fs30}This is your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.18,0:38:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到会有人\N{\fs30}I thought this room was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.52,0:38:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是乘长途夜车来的\N{\fs30}I arrived on the night coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.94,0:38:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还认识我吗？我是你的远方表姐\N{\fs30}Don't you recognize me? I'm a distant cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是爱莎\N{\fs30}Call me Elsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.53,0:38:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.45,0:38:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...我的兄长\N{\fs30}And this is... my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.70,0:38:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库\N{\fs30}Eaglet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.71,0:39:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子 是我占了\N{\fs30}I've taken your room...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.21,0:39:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的房间\N{\fs30}it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里挺适合你的\N{\fs30}You're welcome to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.38,0:39:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不可以 再给我找一间 可以吗？\N{\fs30}No, I couldn't.You'll find me another, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.72,0:39:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我要问问祖母\N{\fs30}I'll ask Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.05,0:39:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖母出远门了 亲爱的孩子\N{\fs30}Your grandma has gone away,dear child.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.22,0:39:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,告别都没有就走了？\N{\fs30}Without saying good-bye?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.56,0:39:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老年人经常会有古怪的心血来潮\N{\fs30}Old people have their odd whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.36,0:39:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得你会同意我住她的房间的\N{\fs30}But I'm sure you'll allow me to stay in her quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.32,0:39:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,非常乐意\N{\fs30}With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.20,0:39:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那 这个房间 就是你的了\N{\fs30}This room is yours, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.12,0:39:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧\N{\fs30}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好想去骑马啊\N{\fs30}I'd love to go for a horse ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.77,0:39:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的马可以给你骑\N{\fs30}I'll lend you my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.10,0:40:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我很累 我要去休息了\N{\fs30}I'm very tired.I'm going to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.19,0:40:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不认识我吗？\N{\fs30}You really don't recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.24,0:40:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.66,0:40:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不怕我 对吗？\N{\fs30}You're not afraid of me,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.00,0:40:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是自从见到我 亲爱的 你还有...\N{\fs30}But these are silly questions, my dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.26,0:40:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一些傻傻的疑惑\N{\fs30}since we only just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.62,0:42:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的耳环！\N{\fs30}My earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.28,0:43:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹还没有回来？\N{\fs30}Your sister still hasn't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.58,0:43:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉在哪？你肯定知道\N{\fs30}Where's Valerie? You must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.04,0:43:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你生气的样子可爱极了\N{\fs30}You're adorable when you're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.58,0:43:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉在哪？\N{\fs30}Where's Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.42,0:43:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你 但有一个条件\N{\fs30}I'll tell you on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.09,0:43:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须和我做爱\N{\fs30}You must make love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.93,0:43:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能！\N{\fs30}Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.86,0:43:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那你滚出去\N{\fs30}Leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.90,0:43:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.57,0:43:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是你的客人 该你滚！\N{\fs30}I'm not your guest here.You leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.32,0:43:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你会后悔的\N{\fs30}You'll regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你会死的非常体面的\N{\fs30}You will die a glorious death!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.71,0:44:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧 瓦莱莉！\N{\fs30}Die, Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.13,0:44:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧！\N{\fs30}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.22,0:44:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库！\N{\fs30}Eaglet!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.85,0:44:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安了 我的黑发女孩儿\N{\fs30}Good niqht, my dark-haired girl
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.69,0:45:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 做个甜蜜的梦\N{\fs30}Good night and sweet dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.57,0:45:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当你醒来\N{\fs30}When you wake
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.74,0:45:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,爱人啊\N{\fs30}My love
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.87,0:45:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要守护好你的秘密\N{\fs30}Do not reveal your secret
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.75,0:45:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉 你得救了\N{\fs30}Valerie, you're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.50,0:45:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都听到了\N{\fs30}I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.42,0:45:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我表姐爱上你了\N{\fs30}My cousin's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.92,0:45:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-你表姐？ -我知道\N{\fs30}-Your cousin?  -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.67,0:45:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是祖母\N{\fs30}She is Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.89,0:45:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她偷了我的耳环\N{\fs30}She stole my earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.43,0:45:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但那耳环是空的\N{\fs30}But they were empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.39,0:45:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,耳环的真正秘密 在此\N{\fs30}Here lies their secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.35,0:45:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它们会保护你远离危险\N{\fs30}They'll protect you from mortal danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.11,0:45:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要提防黄鼠狼\N{\fs30}Beware of the Polecat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.98,0:45:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪？\N{\fs30}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.82,0:45:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-他要死了  -可怜的\N{\fs30}-He's dying.  -Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.24,0:45:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他蛊惑了你\N{\fs30}He's bewitched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.37,0:45:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.33,0:45:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs30}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.75,0:46:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不行！ 我们是兄妹！\N{\fs30}No, you mustn't! We're brother and sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.67,0:46:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-主教也是你的父亲  -这不是真的！\N{\fs30}-The bishop was our father.  -That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.13,0:46:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,回来！\N{\fs30}Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.22,0:46:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉！黄鼠狼才是我的父亲\N{\fs30}Valerie! The Polecat is my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.06,0:46:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我会 我不会\N{\fs30}I will, I will not
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.61,0:47:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会！\N{\fs30}I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.48,0:47:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要死了！\N{\fs30}I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.57,0:47:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要死了！\N{\fs30}I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.90,0:47:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道 老是什么滋味了吧\N{\fs30}Now you know what it's like to be old.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.16,0:47:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用白费口舌了\N{\fs30}You're wasting your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.25,0:47:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉也要死了\N{\fs30}Valerie's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.25,0:48:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我的青春 我牺牲了她\N{\fs30}I sacrificed her for my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.67,0:48:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你终将会死 像我一样\N{\fs30}You're doomed just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.14,0:48:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会经历这般的抽搐\N{\fs30}You'll suffer the same convulsions.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.10,0:48:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你的孙女 可以拯救我们\N{\fs30}Only your granddaughter could have saved us both,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.77,0:48:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他流着我的血\N{\fs30}because she has my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.77,0:48:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能？她的父亲是主教\N{\fs30}How could that be? Her father was the bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.86,0:48:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是主教！\N{\fs30}I was the bishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.99,0:48:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瓦莱莉的父亲！\N{\fs30}I'm Valerie's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.49,0:48:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你撒谎\N{\fs30}You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.41,0:48:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喝的！\N{\fs30}Something to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.79,0:48:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不准！\N{\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.58,0:48:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,先告诉我 如何延续我的青春\N{\fs30}First tell me how to prolong my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.67,0:48:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,救瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Save Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.55,0:48:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她的血里藏着 我们的得救法门\N{\fs30}In her blood lies our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.34,0:48:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.68,0:48:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌的瓦莱莉！\N{\fs30}Cursed Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.10,0:49:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fs30}It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.61,0:49:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fs30}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.15,0:49:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子\N{\fs30}My child.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.49,0:49:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs30}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.00,0:49:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这令我作呕！\N{\fs30}No, it's too disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.46,0:49:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我又重回人身了\N{\fs30}I'm just a man again,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.63,0:49:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我难逃一死\N{\fs30}and I must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.30,0:49:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不会死\N{\fs30}No, you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.17,0:50:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我\N{\fs30}You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.75,0:50:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲！\N{\fs30}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.09,0:50:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-放开我！  -我又回复魔鬼身了！\N{\fs30}-Let me go! -I'm a monster again!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.60,0:50:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我！\N{\fs30}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.10,0:50:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我！\N{\fs30}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.23,0:50:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.38,0:51:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉西恩！\N{\fs30}Gracian!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.93,0:51:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的格拉西恩！\N{\fs30}My Gracian!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.15,0:51:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的爱人睡得沉如朽木\N{\fs30}Your lover is sleeping like a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.99,0:51:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉西恩！\N{\fs30}Gracián.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.33,0:52:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的格拉西恩！\N{\fs30}Poor Gracián.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.70,0:52:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个主意 爱莎\N{\fs30}I have a plan, Elsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.38,0:52:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要奥利库的心\N{\fs30}I need Eaglet's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.71,0:52:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你要杀了奥利库？\N{\fs30}You mean to kill Eaglet?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.92,0:52:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心能使我的女儿复生 并使她的永远年轻\N{\fs30}His heart will revive my daughter and give her eternal youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.84,0:52:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,理查德 将奥利库的心移植给我吧\N{\fs30}Richard, transplant Eaglet's heart into my breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.64,0:52:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你想背叛瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}You're betraying Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.98,0:52:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,理查德 你会照我说的做的\N{\fs30}Richard, you'll do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.32,0:52:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,用血淋淋的心\N{\fs30}With a bleeding heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.70,0:52:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库\N{\fs30}Eaglet...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.71,0:52:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么会舍弃你？\N{\fs30}why did I abandon you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.31,0:53:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！\N{\fs30}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.86,0:53:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你的鬼魂为什么缠着我不放 瓦莱莉？\N{\fs30}Why do you haunt me, Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.07,0:53:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要怕\N{\fs30}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.99,0:53:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我没死 你也还活着\N{\fs30}I'm not dead,and neither are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.78,0:53:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来 我带你出去\N{\fs30}Come.I'll lead you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.00,0:53:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着这条路就到教区了 神父\N{\fs30}The rectory is across the way, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.13,0:53:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是你勾引我犯罪 邪恶的女孩！\N{\fs30}You tempted me to sin,wicked girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.42,0:53:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你会受到惩罚的\N{\fs30}You will get your due.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.14,0:53:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,“瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}“Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.23,0:53:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说再见了\N{\fs30}this is good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.15,0:54:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你抛弃了我\N{\fs30}You abandoned me,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.19,0:54:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼亵渎了你的唇\N{\fs30}and that monster defiled your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.11,0:54:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本该幸福的在一起\N{\fs30}We could have been so happy together
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.62,0:54:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Trust me, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.66,0:54:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,黄鼠狼不是你的父亲 也不是我的父亲\N{\fs30}the Polecat is neither your father nor mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.96,0:54:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你延续了他的命\N{\fs30}You've prolonged his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.25,0:54:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成为你的守护者 朋友甚至丈夫 但是太迟了\N{\fs30}I wanted to be your protector, friend,and husband, but it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.92,0:54:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了 瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Farewell, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.80,0:54:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你的奥利库\N{\fs30}Your Eaglet.”
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.47,0:54:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉 怎么了？来\N{\fs30}Valerie, what's wrong? Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.56,0:54:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,海德维卡！\N{\fs30}Hedvika!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.57,0:54:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,海德维卡\N{\fs30}Hedvika.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.11,0:54:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？\N{\fs30}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.99,0:54:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,自结婚起 我日渐消瘦\N{\fs30}I've been wasting away since my wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.08,0:55:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-你得多吃点  -不\N{\fs30}-You must eat hearty soups.  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.63,0:55:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我被吸血鬼控制了\N{\fs30}I'm in a vampire's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.02,0:55:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉\N{\fs30}Valerie...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.73,0:55:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的肩头\N{\fs30}look at my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.66,0:55:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,疼吗？\N{\fs30}Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.57,0:55:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼\N{\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.37,0:55:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-你注意我的嘴唇了吗？  -没有 怎么了？\N{\fs30}-You notice anything about my lips?  -No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.70,0:55:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的嘴不脏吗？\N{\fs30}Aren't they stained?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.54,0:55:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定是吃了浆果\N{\fs30}You've been eating berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.05,0:55:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和你在一起 我什么都不怕\N{\fs30}When you're with me,I'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.93,0:55:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我很开心\N{\fs30}I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.14,0:55:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来都没有亲近的女友\N{\fs30}I've never had a close girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.09,0:56:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱莉 我得救了！\N{\fs30}Valerie, I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.18,0:56:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看 咬痕消失了\N{\fs30}Look. The marks are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.77,0:56:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你得吻让我恢复了健康\N{\fs30}Your kisses have restored my health.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.23,0:56:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你真美\N{\fs30}You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.36,0:56:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个巫女生活在你们当中\N{\fs30}There's a witch living among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.11,0:56:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她用淫言秽语折磨我\N{\fs30}She tormented me with her sinful words.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.33,0:56:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她用嘴唇讨好我 亲蚀我\N{\fs30}She pressed her fawning hips against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.45,0:57:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当她发现 我勇敢的抵挡住了她的诱惑\N{\fs30}When she saw that I could bravely resist her temptations,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.50,0:57:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她就想用绳套勒死我\N{\fs30}she threw a noose around my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.25,0:57:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝 我安全的逃了出来\N{\fs30}I thank God that I escaped safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.68,0:57:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那个巫女\N{\fs30}But that witch
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.47,0:57:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就藏在你们当中！\N{\fs30}is now hiding among you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.06,0:57:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把她交出来！她必须承受火刑！\N{\fs30}Hand her over! She must burn at the stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.77,0:57:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他说谎！不要信他！\N{\fs30}That's a lie! Don't believe him!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.48,0:57:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,巫女在这儿呢！\N{\fs30}There's the witch now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.86,0:57:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要信他的话！ 我发誓 他在说谎！\N{\fs30}Don't believe him! I swear he's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.82,0:57:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开 撒旦！\N{\fs30}Begone, Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.66,0:57:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住她！绑到柱子上！\N{\fs30}Seize her! To the stake with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.35,0:58:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,承认你是巫女吧！\N{\fs30}Confess that you're a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.64,0:58:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！纵火犯！\N{\fs30}Liar! Pyromaniac!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.14,0:58:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,忏悔吧！\N{\fs30}Repent!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.86,0:58:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,长着歪毛胡子的小丑！\N{\fs30}Hairy-faced clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.72,0:59:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利库 为何弃我于不顾？\N{\fs30}Eaglet, why hast thou forsaken me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.69,1:00:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她来了！ 多美啊！\N{\fs30}Here she Is! She's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.76,1:00:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的主人们 旅途归来\N{\fs30}Our masters,back from their travels,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.30,1:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,将先出他们的手 他的脚\N{\fs30}will give us their hands and feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.18,1:00:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的脑袋要休息\N{\fs30}They will rest their heads,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.60,1:00:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将献上我们的吻\N{\fs30}and we will kiss them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.78,1:01:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到这来 你们这些娼妇！\N{\fs30}Come here, you trollops!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.95,1:01:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要挨揍吗？\N{\fs30}You ever had a good thrashing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.18,1:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,畜生！\N{\fs30}Beast!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.25,1:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,干了这杯酒 理查德\N{\fs30}Drink deeply, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.83,1:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了！\N{\fs30}He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.80,1:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是黄鼠狼！\N{\fs30}The Polecat!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.24,1:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,愿魔咒得破\N{\fs30}May the power of these spells be broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.56,1:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安了 我的黑发女孩儿\N{\fs30}Good niqht, my dark-haired girl
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.61,1:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 做个美梦\N{\fs30}Good night and sweet dreams
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.74,1:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,当你醒来 我的爱人\N{\fs30}When you wake, my love
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.83,1:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要守护好你的秘密\N{\fs30}Do not reveal your secret
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.70,1:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母！\N{\fs30}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.58,1:05:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了？\N{\fs30}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.71,1:05:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 孩子？ 我去教堂了啊\N{\fs30}Where do you think, child? I was at church.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.59,1:05:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,传教士们都走了？\N{\fs30}Have the missionaries gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.98,1:05:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么传教士？\N{\fs30}What missionaries?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.31,1:05:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 我的孩子？\N{\fs30}What's the matter, my child?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.78,1:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 祖母\N{\fs30}Nothing, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.43,1:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母？\N{\fs30}Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.18,1:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有个怪人\N{\fs30}There's a strange man outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.35,1:06:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一个在镇上转悠的戏子\N{\fs30}That's just one of the actors wandering around the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.59,1:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我 最亲爱的\N{\fs30}My dearest...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.26,1:06:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去剧院\N{\fs30}do not go to the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.38,1:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,相反\N{\fs30}Instead..
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.09,1:07:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,即刻跃上马背\N{\fs30}have the horses hitched up at once
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.06,1:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奔向蓝湖\N{\fs30}and drive to the Blue Lake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.45,1:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪 上帝啊！\N{\fs30}Don't shoot, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.28,1:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.05,1:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐！\N{\fs30}Miss!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.05,1:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你祖母不行了！\N{\fs30}Your grandma is dying!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.51,1:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母！\N{\fs30}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.43,1:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,最亲爱的祖母 你怎么了？\N{\fs30}Dearest Grandma, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.94,1:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母\N{\fs30}Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.03,1:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,镜子\N{\fs30}The mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.55,1:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无人驾驶的马车 自己驶出了庭院\N{\fs30}A coach with no coachman has left the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.39,1:08:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好兆头\N{\fs30}That's a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.98,1:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直没有勇气告诉你真相\N{\fs30}I've never had the courage to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.82,1:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妈妈爱上了某个猎场守门人\N{\fs30}Your mother loved a certain young gamekeeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.54,1:08:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为他生育了两个孩子\N{\fs30}She gave him two children,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.63,1:08:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一男一女\N{\fs30}a boy and a girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.34,1:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 理查德 我的情人 告诉我孩子是他的\N{\fs30}But Richard, my lover,told me the children were his,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.59,1:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,出于妒忌\N{\fs30}and out of jealousy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.18,1:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你的妈妈赶出了这个家\N{\fs30}I drove your mother from this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.68,1:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下了小女儿\N{\fs30}I kept the little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.44,1:09:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你\N{\fs30}You are that girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.52,1:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,理查德带走了奥利库 不知所踪\N{\fs30}Richard took Eaglet away to some unknown place.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.32,1:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,赶你妈妈出门的时候 我说\N{\fs30}I drove your mother out with the words...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.36,1:09:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“有超一日 如果马儿\N{\fs30}“I'll take you back
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.78,1:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,自己将你带回来 我就接受你”\N{\fs30}when the horses bring you back on their own.”
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.53,1:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那 我的母亲还活着？\N{\fs30}Then my mother's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.50,1:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母！\N{\fs30}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.41,1:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲！\N{\fs30}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.03,1:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子\N{\fs30}My child.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.30,1:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你父亲 亲爱的\N{\fs30}This is your father, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.80,1:10:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像在哪儿见过你 父亲\N{\fs30}I've seen your face somewhere before, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.64,1:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是你婴儿时的记忆\N{\fs30}An early childhood memory,no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.41,1:10:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切 不会是一场梦吧？\N{\fs30}Is all this but a dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.75,1:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿你的祖母能原谅我\N{\fs30}If only your grandmother would forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.89,1:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安了 我的魔法师\N{\fs30}Good night, my wizard
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.35,1:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听听你的精灵 如何哭泣\N{\fs30}Hear your fairy, how she cries
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.02,1:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听她哭的 多么绝望\N{\fs30}Hear her cry so hopelessly
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.45,1:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚为她抖起悲伤的披肩\N{\fs30}The night weaves a cloak of grief for her
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.00,1:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安了 我的黑发女孩儿\N{\fs30}Good niqht, my dark-haired girl
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.50,1:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs30}Good night
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.21,1:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,做个美梦\N{\fs30}And sweet dreams
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.88,1:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当你醒来 我的爱人\N{\fs30}When you wake, my love
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.35,1:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,千万要守好自己的秘密\N{\fs30}Do not reveal your secret
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.06,1:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,完

